org.deeplearning4j.models.sequencevectors.iterators

Class FilteredSequenceIterator<T extends SequenceElement>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.models.sequencevectors.iterators.FilteredSequenceIterator<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SequenceIterator<T>

    public class FilteredSequenceIterator<T extends SequenceElement>
extends java.lang.Object
implements SequenceIterator<T>
    This implementation of SequenceIterator passes each sequence through specified vocabulary, filtering out SequenceElements that are not available in Vocabulary. Please note: nextSequence() method can return empty sequence, if none of elements were found in attached vocabulary.
